metadata.name: Lonely Tree
metadata.description:
Sink your roots deeply into Earth.
Reflect, meditate and take chances.
Feel the wind and the sea breeze lifting your spirits.
Stand tall and proud, 
like a lonely tree on an island of hope & dreams.

Artist: Vladimiro Rodrigues

Medium: PNG 5184 x 3456 

B&W Photography created in South Fjords of Norway
